name: D i v ! n g   H i g h
description: I drew with my roommate at the window watching the street. We listened to nostalgic songs and remembered one that I liked a lot. She said it sounded like a 2001 soundtrack. It's my favorite book. I really wanted to be in that book, heading into the unknown in the solar system in search of something I still don't know exactly what it is. You know... being able to say “it's that they called me earlier and said I need to go”.
